{"tid":146673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普簽署行政命令 禁6國公民申請入境","createTime":"2017-03-07T09:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T10:11:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b75045a44067cd02e519170e841dc95ba6f84fc9","tid":146673,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/03/07/1506557_d7e5ef4b577912e8d23dcd5900ab9cee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F1506557_d7e5ef4b577912e8d23dcd5900ab9cee.jpg&h=40661a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署新的行政命令，禁止6個國家公民申請簽證入境。公布消息的美國國務卿蒂勒森表示，新的禁令是要增強美國的國境保護能力。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在1月簽署行政命令，禁止7個國家的公民申請簽證入境。但美國有團體入稟，取得法庭頒布阻止該行政命令的執行。<br />\n<br />\n根據白宮公布，新的行政命令將於3月16日生效，受影響的6個國家包括蘇丹、敍利亞、伊朗、利比亞、索馬里及也門。伊拉克獲剔除出名單。禁令為期90日。<br />\n<br />\n根據新行政命令，美國難民入境計劃會暫停工作120天，日後恢復後，2017年接收難民人數將是每年5萬人。去年，奧巴馬政府接收1萬名敍利亞難民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/1506557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2FarticlePrint%2Fid%2F1506557&d=kDoZHsh44GLEl9RERzeBg7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f8f9b54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/1506557</a>"},{"pid":"3496e1def14f3fc3b55d9a3198f43525a36a5237","tid":146673,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"TRUMP TRUMP都要跪低去修改~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證明選舉時得把口係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當時講到統治全世界咁~ 家下咪一樣要向現實低頭~係D傻豬豬先信佢~<br />\n<br />\n睇下今次會唔會又被人BAN~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514d87a526c42a0317e00b2cf1b62a9f4cc23547","tid":146673,"uid":53677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>TRUMP TRUMP都要跪低去修改~ <img src=\"/asse